Class QuizController

java.lang.Object
com.github.ilim.backend.controller.QuizController
@RestController public class QuizController extends Object
REST controller responsible for managing quizzes.

Provides endpoints for retrieving quizzes, adding new quizzes to modules, updating existing quizzes, and removing quizzes from modules.

    • findQuizById

      @GetMapping("/quiz/{quizId}") public ApiRes<Res<QuizDto>> findQuizById(@AuthenticationPrincipal org.springframework.security.oauth2.jwt.Jwt jwt, @PathVariable UUID quizId)
      Retrieves a quiz by its unique identifier.

      Fetches the quiz details for the specified quiz ID, accessible to authenticated users.

      Parameters:
      jwt - the JWT token representing the authenticated user
      quizId - the unique identifier of the quiz to retrieve
      Returns:
      an ApiRes containing the QuizDto representing the quiz details

    • addQuizToModule

      @PostMapping("/instructor/module/{moduleId}/add-quiz") @PreAuthorize("hasRole('INSTRUCTOR')") public ApiRes<Res<String>> addQuizToModule(@AuthenticationPrincipal org.springframework.security.oauth2.jwt.Jwt jwt, @PathVariable UUID moduleId, @Valid @RequestBody @Valid QuizDto dto)
      Adds a new quiz to a specific module.

      Accepts a QuizDto containing quiz details, associates it with the specified module ID, and adds the quiz to the module.

      Parameters:
      jwt - the JWT token representing the authenticated instructor
      moduleId - the unique identifier of the module to which the quiz will be added
      dto - the quiz data transfer object containing quiz details
      Returns:
      an ApiRes containing a success message upon successful addition of the quiz

    • updateQuiz

      @PutMapping("/instructor/update-quiz/{quizId}") @PreAuthorize("hasRole('INSTRUCTOR')") public ApiRes<Res<String>> updateQuiz(@AuthenticationPrincipal org.springframework.security.oauth2.jwt.Jwt jwt, @PathVariable UUID quizId, @Valid @RequestBody @Valid QuizDto dto)
      Updates an existing quiz with new details.

      Accepts a QuizDto containing updated quiz details, associates it with the specified quiz ID, and updates the quiz accordingly.

      Parameters:
      jwt - the JWT token representing the authenticated instructor
      quizId - the unique identifier of the quiz to update
      dto - the quiz data transfer object containing updated quiz details
      Returns:
      an ApiRes containing a success message upon successful update of the quiz

    • removeQuizFromModule

      @DeleteMapping("/instructor/delete-quiz/{quizId}") @PreAuthorize("hasRole('INSTRUCTOR')") public ApiRes<Res<String>> removeQuizFromModule(@AuthenticationPrincipal org.springframework.security.oauth2.jwt.Jwt jwt, @PathVariable UUID quizId)
      Removes a quiz from a specific module.

      Deletes the association between the specified quiz ID and its module, effectively removing the quiz.

      Parameters:
      jwt - the JWT token representing the authenticated instructor
      quizId - the unique identifier of the quiz to remove
      Returns:
      an ApiRes containing a success message upon successful removal of the quiz
